description: Coreanos - The perfect harmony of savory Korean BBQ with the familiar flavors of Mexican cuisine.Every item on our menu delivers a unique flavor experience with every bite.  Indulge your taste buds in some mouthwatering goodness.   Your mouth will surely thank you.Coreanos is the perfect choice for catering any type of event in the Houston Area. Since we operate out of our state-of-the-art food truck, we have the ability to offer a custom, gourmet menu of which is cooked and served fresh and hot to your event attendees!
